Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about a dialogue system and its training using deep reinforcement learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the development of an intelligent interactive agent. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses deep reinforcement learning for training the dialogue system. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is possible as the paper discusses the development of a software system for dialogue control. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also possible as the paper uses deep reinforcement learning, which is a type of neural computing.
